and just now.. 7:00. He's so cute though, he was sleeping on my bed and when he had to go to the bathroom he'd like keep hitting me with his paw and then when I was awake he'd go to my bedroom door. Aww.

This week ROCKED. Went to our game on Monday night.. we won. FIRST TIME EVER IN THE PLAYOFFS! Went to our game Tuesday night.. lost. Don't even want to say by how much. We had no chance. I mean we rock HARD and all.. but Agawam was just too good. :( After that.. slept over Stephs house. Then we went to subway and Lianne gave us free sodas and cookies! :) YAY FOR SUBWAY! Then we went back to Stephs and slept there.. THEN AT 8:00 WE WENT TO SOME STORE TO GET MILK WITH OUR PAJAMAS ON!! HAHA... then we went home and set up for another bake sale. WHICH WE RAISED $15! Haha..
OK.. I have to scram. LEAVE ME SOME COMMENTS IF YOU LOVE ME <33

OOOOWWWW!! I just got stung by a bee. :(:( It hurt WICKED WICKED bad. It stung me on my pinkie toe. Grahh. OK.. so yesterday was WICKED fun. Spent most of the day at the park, hanging out with Nikiss, Swartsy, Meg, and Delia. Niki tried to teach me how to catch a ball with a double play or something LOL.. Then Kelly [Sha-nay-nay] and Sarah came, and we went to go to the High School to MEET SOMEONE WHO WAS SUPPOSED TO BE THERE. Well.. thats it for yesterday. Today=NOTHING. I'll update more later..

Yeah.. today was a pretty boring day. HighlightS of the day: 1. Talking to STEPH FINALLY! 2. Ari telling that the book was great. :) Didn't do much today.. kinda just sat around. Finished cleaning the horse stalls, went swimming.. not much more. Oh yeah, my mom went to get a hiarcut. Fun fun. Also- my brother had a friend [Adam] sleep over last night.. and I was awoken this morning at 7:30 by Febreeze being sprayed all over my head. I pretented to continue sleeping, hoping they'd go away. But no. They proceeded to chuck little plastic army people at my head. Then they realized that the army men were all over my bed and that if they wanted them back they'd have to sneak in somehow. So they decided to "creep" [aka bash into the bed and giggle] under my bed and hide there until they had a plan. So when I felt little hands all over my feet searching for the stupid toys.. I finally woke up and punched Dougie. He left.

Yeah, so now its 5:30 and my brother went to All*Star practice and we're waiting till he gets back to go get food somewhere.
